 brain. She says this may be because things like fast-twitch muscle fibres =
which enable our physical ability to respond quickly,&nbsp;<a target=3D"_bl=
ank" href=3D"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7493202" class=3D"sc-f9178328-=
0 iCaRzc">have waned</a>, or because our mitochondria =E2=80=93 the compone=
